Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:41.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With the first month of the new year,\Nyou will finally come of age...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and you will be permitted to wear\Na sword within the imperial court.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:47.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are aware of this, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:48.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:54.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As your father, I intend to\Nbestow a sword upon you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:03.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sagum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May you wear it in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:17.30,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 15\NUntimely Death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"The sign of the great drought..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:33.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...which appears once\Nevery hundred years..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:38.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...is a natural consequence of the\Naged Nyunga Ro Im approaching death."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Natural consequence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that is true, then perhaps we\Ncannot determine if the prince is alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:49.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...using only the sign of\Nthe great drought as a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:26.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, you're not a young woman\Nany more. You shouldn't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,None of your cheek, youngster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:32.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when you can't get\Nto the truth unless you push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a craving for yamabime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:45.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boy. Fetch me some yamabime\Nfrom the mountains out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamabime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, you don't even\Nknow what yamabime are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're a purple fruit with\Na clean split down the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:04:00.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go onto any mountain and you'll\Nfind them hanging from trees all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and fetch me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find some right away\Nonce you reach the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:32.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said that the egg\Nwouldn't harm its guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The egg won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:43.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that you\Nhaven't told us yet, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:48.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say anything\Nwith the boy sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:54.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, something called "Rarunga"\Nis going to come here from Nayug.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I wasn't able\Nto learn anything specific...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:04.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but the Yona Ro Gai\Ncalled it an egg-eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:08.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if\Nit's a living creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a chance that it\Nwill attack him right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:23.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just hide Chagum\Nsomewhere until the egg hatches?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it can't hatch\Nunless it's taken to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...something called\Nthe Land of Feasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Land of Feasting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:35.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This must be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:51.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand,\NI did learn when the egg will hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say it'll be on\NSagu's spring day of equality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spring day of equality?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The vernal equinox, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the day when day\Nand night are the same length.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:08.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They said that on that day, the boy\Nhimself will explain everything to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:15.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, the boy will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:19.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The egg-eater probably won't\Nturn up until sometime around then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:23.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting around here talking\Nabout it isn't going to help matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:30.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start by finding out\Nwho or what this Rarunga is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:35.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I can't go back to the Knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:41.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just hope that there's still\Nsomething for us to go on out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well!\NYou found some big ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're awfully light\Nfor something so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are plump and ripe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:05.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I was a young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:09.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...the storytelling hag of the village\Noften sent me out to pick these for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:15.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Yakoo storyteller\Nmight know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:21.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All the Yakoo around here have pretty\Nmuch assimilated into Yogoan culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:25.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that the oral histories they tell\Nhave been handed down accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about Toumi village?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:34.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The old oral histories\Nmight have survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...out in the village\Nmy grandfather moved to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:42.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, it might be worth going\Nout to that godforsaken village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than sitting\Naround doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, on a journey to\Nget some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A journey? That sounds like\Nsomething to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you'll go check it out, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:09.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop by home first to\Nmake the necessary preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to pick up\Nsome medicinal herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:27.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"And then, mammatus clouds appeared\Nto allow the mother water spirit..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...to bestow her final blessing\Nupon the egg, her child."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:35.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"And then, mammatus clouds appeared\Nto allow the mother water spirit..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...to bestow her final blessing\Nupon the egg, her child"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:44.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Exactly as described in Yakooan oral\Ntradition, on the last day of summer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...clouds shaped like breasts\Nappeared directly above the village..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:52.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...where the guardian of the\Nspirit lived, blotting out the sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Almost as if the earth\Nwas swallowing them..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:58.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...every cloud in the sky was drawn\Nto a single point on the ground..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...after which a localized\Ndownpour began to fall."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! If I can\Nobserve these clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it will be the proof I need\Nthat Prince Chagum is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What day is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Shuga?\NIs everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The master star reader\Nstill has the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:15.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds as if you have\Nuncovered something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:19.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must get out of here\Nat once to verify something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, sir.\NWe will try to find a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:26.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our apologies, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:48.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:57.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have our deepest\Napologies, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you treat the master\Nstar reader with such disrespect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has the heat gone to your head?\NSuch a lack of discipline!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry back to your station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:31.02,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:43.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you entered\Nthese chambers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you\Nare referring to, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:50.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I take it that you realize the consequences\Nof entering here without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:58.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pity. In your ten years of service...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:03.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you have never once committed an\Noffense. I never expected to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Become empty vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry. This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:30.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We wish for nothing more than\NPrince Chagum's safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure that my\Ncomrade has no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:55.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sword the mikado gave you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:14:00.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a bit different than\Nthe style you prefer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:06.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The success of a gift is determined by\Nthe attention given to it by the recipient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:10.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is important is the sentiment\Nof the giver and recipient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:24.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The day that signals summer's end...\NIf that is today, this very day, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:39.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The prince is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:59.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is he alive,\Nhe is right under our noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right here in Kosenkyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a downpour...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:38.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a long time since\Nyou were here last, Shuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One's senses are always heightened\Nwhen one is pressed for time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:53.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling,\NYour Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because I've been\Nso focused. I am feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does something trouble you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:04.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps my spirit is\Nsomewhat exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:11.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Playing the role of Crown Prince\NSagum has taken its toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:15.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With some effort,\NI have managed to endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but it now takes every\Nounce of my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:23.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, perhaps you might\Ndelegate some of your duties to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:26.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and lessen the\Nburden placed on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:32.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there were a few people\Nwho were truly able to support me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:41.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To make matters worse,\NI lack a certain crucial quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:47.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The divine grace to captivate\Npeople's hearts and not let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I might use my rank to\Nsway people to action...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:53.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but it is rather difficult\Nto sway their hearts as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:57.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was Chagum who had this quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:00.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He had the innate\Nability to charm others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:04.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness,\NPrince Chagum is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum is no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:14.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it is because he is gone that I am\Nable to keep going without breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will do his share, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry. I did not mean\Nto bore you with trivialities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:30.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If speaking with me lifts your spirits,\NI shall come whenever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:34.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You will? I do feel\Nsomewhat better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:37.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuga, I hope you will\Ncontinue to be a good friend to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:41.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:46.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what is it that\Nyou wished to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:51.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Your Highness.\NI should have exercised better judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will call upon you another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:25.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend the use of\Na horse for three days or so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:32.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time a star reader\Nhas ever borrowed a horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:36.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry.\NI come from a family of fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've ridden my share of horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:47.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, that's quite\Na tan you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I think his skin's\Ndarker than it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:54.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look a little more\Nmuscular now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:59.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't had\Nany strange dreams lately, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like a huge weight has\Nbeen lifted from my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about how\NI'm free to live my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...as I see fit from\Nnow on, I get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:13.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something\Nthat you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to do something\Nto help other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and also learn about\Nthings that interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:23.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have the\Ntemperament of a scholar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:28.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so maybe you should become a\Nfield scholar and teach the local children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:33.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, maybe I'll buy him a writing\Ndesk so that he can read and write.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:47.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What we learned...\NAre you going to tell Chagum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:51.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I'll probably have\Nno choice but to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:55.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at the moment,\Nwe don't know anything for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a map to Toumi village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:21.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I uncover proof that\NPrince Chagum is still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and report my findings\Nto the master star reader...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...everything will work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Sagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:48.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This correspondence\Nhas just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:52.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gakai, I find myself\Na bit exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:02.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have taught me\Na great many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:05.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:08.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are too kind, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:14.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I want you to\Ncooperate with Shuga as a star reader...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and make the palace\Na better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:21.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:23.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:28.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you release\Nthat bird into the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:35.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can no longer give it\Nthe attention it deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:42.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Considering all your duties\Nas crown prince, perhaps it is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His Highness commands you to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Fly, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:56.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on... Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is flying strongly, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:21.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely the result of the\Ntender care you lavished upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:27.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:35.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Chagum...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:45.61,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.31,0:24:46.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuga, who has been given full command\Nover the search for Chagum...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.41,0:24:49.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...once again sets the Hunters\Nloose upon Ogi no Shimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.82,0:24:53.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\N"With All one's Heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 16\NWith All One's Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.49,0:24:56.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The unforgettable summer\Nis about to come to an end.
